      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/17/168",
      "text": [
        " «يَتَوَضَّأُ ثُمَّ يَنْضِحُ ثَوْبَهُ فِي اَلنَّهَارِ مَرَّةً وَاحِدَةً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.168 - Abu Al-Hasan Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) was asked about a eunuch who experiences difficulty with urination and notices wetness repeatedly.\nImam (as) replied: 'He should perform ablution and sprinkle his clothing with water once during the day.'."
        ]
      }
